Program: Outlook
Title: The Human Face of War in the Middle East
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbshl
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
A return to Haifa and Beirut to talk to two people about their experience of life there during the current war. Also, the blind people who will benefit from the Equal Opportunities Bill passed in Ghana. The man bringing Iraqi children to Great Britain to play football. Tribal conflict in Assam.